        {
            "title": "澳新銀行:中國的「不良」通脹仍優於通縮",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/CfH_FWIuK6zxDmMIwU.AYA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXNPEC290AN_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com- <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"澳新銀行\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:澳新銀行;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/澳新銀行\">澳新銀行</a>分析師週三在一份報告中表示,中國可能會比市場預期更早地擺脫長期通縮週期,重返正值價格指標,儘管復甦可能伴隨挑戰。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">澳新銀行表示,預計中國的生產者價格指數(PPI)、消費者價格指數(CPI)和GDP平減指數將在2026年第一季度全部轉為同比正增長,其中GDP平減指數預計將上升約0.5%,這將是三年來的首次擴張。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這一轉變主要由輸入性通脹推動,特別是能源價格上漲,分析師將其描述為「不良」通脹,因為它可能會擠壓本已疲弱的消費和工業盈利能力。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-cbd62a4f-fc90-3d79-9b8a-7cbe2ccb21ad-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">然而,澳新銀行表示,這種通脹仍優於通縮,後者一直是由中國經濟中供需持續失衡所驅動。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">澳新銀行分析師表示:「中國在管理成本方面擁有豐富的專業知識和資源,但提振消費的能力有限。」他們指出,政策制定者在應對成本上升方面比應對價格下跌更具優勢。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該行表示,油價上漲可能會支撐可再生能源等特定板塊的需求,但不太可能解決更廣泛的經濟失衡問題,同時也會對家庭支出造成壓力。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">預計政策制定者將依賴一系列工具來管理通脹壓力,包括行政管控、動用戰略石油儲備、財政補貼以及努力實現能源進口多元化。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">澳新銀行補充稱,中國可能會繼續在其再通脹策略下推進供給側改革,旨在結束通縮週期,作為建立更統一全國市場努力的一部分。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%BE%B3%E6%96%B0%E9%8A%80%E8%A1%8C-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%9A%84-%E4%B8%8D%E8%89%AF-%E9%80%9A%E8%84%B9%E4%BB%8D%E5%84%AA%E6%96%BC%E9%80%9A%E7%B8%AE-053414087.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-09 14:13:11",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "理財葉師傅｜港股後市仍有波動機會 過夜部署風險高｜Gary Sir",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/jlgZHeFzehCaz3eHx7TRhA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/vi/bossmind_356/259e03b8c6df2451f0970c212abb27e2\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國總統以摧毀伊朗文明的極限施壓下，美伊達成兩星期的停火協議，為美伊中止衝突帶來曙光。環球市場避險情緒減退，恒指周三抽升3%至25,893點。不過，美伊衝突最終能否長期停火仍具有不確定性，後市波動性仍高。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美伊兩國雖暫時停火，但兩國各自開出的談判條件相信難以令對方接受，談判破裂再開打的機會仍存。短期港股料波動性仍強，只宜作即市短炒，過夜部署的風險尚高。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">個股方面，小米（1810）周三大幅反彈6%，但要再進一步向上的難度不小，上方阻力位分別在33.3元及35.48元。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-f0fd7c9f-d1ec-3392-a5b3-8e30685d7b95-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">泡泡瑪特（9992）低位彈高近8%，但該股仍處下跌趨勢兼能量仍低，不宜追入。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美團（3690）有見底反彈跡象，但能量尚欠不足，待升穿90元後才追入也不遲。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美元下跌，黃金回升至近4,800美元，短期有力重上5,000美元水平，但若要再向上突破，則須更多利好因素。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>Gary Sir 資深投資者<br/>註：專欄作家言論不代表本網立場</strong></p><a class=\"mb-module-gap\" data-ylk=\"elm:img;elmt:link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;\" href=\"https://signup.hkiei.com/garysir_bossmind\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/u_lbyPKtHpHAwJ7JKtEUSg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTExMDI-/https://media.zenfs.com/vi/bossmind_356/ba913bad9cf2ad999d7d1518edb55e0c\" width=\"892\"/></div></a></div>",
